description.name: Hotel Blue Tower
description.description: Welcome to Blue Tower hotel, the symbol of modern Dragolm. No matter if you come for a business trip, a conference or just for vacation - this is the right place to stay at. Our rooms are cosy, air conditioned and equipped with design furniture. It goes without saying that all of them have private social facilities. Upon request, we can pick you up from the Dragolm airport, provide you with representative spaces for any kind of event or even arrange custom catering. For more information, plase use one of the contact channels.
